  "title": "Full time or Part time Sales Executive / Manager",
  "description": "<h5>Job Description &amp; Requirements</h5>\n<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Assist Director Sales and Marketing in planning and executing the sales and marketing plan</li>\n  <li>Work with Marketing Team on the production of sales and marketing collaterals</li>\n  <li>Address technical sales enquiries in the area of waterproofing, urban greenery, landscape engineering and ecological solutions, and client’s feedback on product and services.</li>\n  <li>Arrange to meet potential customers to generate lead</li>\n  <li>Conduct outdoor sales presentations to clients, in seminars and workshops</li>\n  <li>Advise and update Director on sales performance reports and activities such as call reports, weekly sales plans and sales forecasts</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<p>· This is an executive level position with at least 1-2 year relevant work experience</p>\n<p>· Fresh graduates are welcome to apply</p>\n<p>· Proficient with Microsoft Office</p>\n<p>· Candidate must possess /be: Self-motivated - Initiative - Independent - Organization skills - Good interpersonal and communication skills</p>",
